issue.title: On boarding flow
issue.body:
### What has Changed
- The user is logged in __and persisted__ **after** the user is taken from the login flow to the home tab bar

### What's New
- Logout from the SettingsVc
- OnBoardingDirector manages what view controller should be the next Vc depending on what the user has already accepted (location, verify phone number)

### What's Missing
> This checklist has been moved to [this](https://trello.com/c/KKaRgWfp) trello card
- [ ] Populate the images in the tutorial
- [ ] Shorten the descriptions of the tutorial

issue.title: Flagging
issue.body:
## Flagging Logic

- created FlaggingContentItems protocol to store the flaggable items for each viewController
- the FlaggingViewController is alway triggered by an action sheet

## FlaggingViewController

- this screen should be presented in a inside navigation controller modally
- finished conforming to the tableView protocols

## Refactored the following classes, regarding the names & marks

- FlaggingViewController
- StatusPagerTabStripViewController

## Notes

- I feel that the FlaggingViewController initializer is a bit redundant since it asks for user to report and also donation to report(hence we could get the user from the donation object), didn't modify anything here and left out the old implementation
- The flagging logic in StatusPagerTabStripViewController should be double checked to make sure we are flagging the right person (might have made a little mistake here)
- We are missing the Flagging Item titles
- Inside the ViewController there I have left a todo for using the FlaggingService
- I didn't have the chance to test anything
